name: Theron Nett (V)
Lore: 'Experienced smuggler from Ord Mantell. Piloted Red 10 at the Battle of Yavin. Long-time wingman of Garven Dreis.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. During your deploy phase, if piloting Red 10, may target one of your starships; deploy a non-[Theed Palace] astromech or matching pilot aboard target from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.(Original concept by Brian Herold - Minnesota States 2005)',
